show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/gYY9Pb
show.description:
A billionaire hiding behind a false identity and a strong single mother fighting for survival are brought together by the innocent wish of a child.
As love blossoms amidst lies, broken dreams find hope again—but the truth about who “Mr. Oberoi” really is could shatter it all.
This is a heartwarming tale of family, deception, and the courage to begin again.
